<item>
            <title>[FLINK-2007] Initial data point in Delta function needs to be serializable</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-2007</link>
                <project id="12315522" key="FLINK">Flink</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Currently we expect the data point passed to the delta function to be serializable, which breaks the serialization assumptions provided in other parts of the code.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This information should be properly serialized by Flink serializers instead.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
